als|country=GBR||sep=,|GCMG}} || 19 February 1883 || 5 March 1889 || {{age in years and days|1883|02|19|1889|03|05}}\n|-\n| 12|| [[Image:Algernon Keith-Falconer.jpg|80px]] || [[Algernon Keith-Falconer, 9th Earl of Kintore|The Rt Hon. Earl of Kintore]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR||sep=,|GCMG}} || 11 April 1889 || 10 April 1895 || {{age in years and days|1889|04|11|1895|04|10}}\n|-\n| 13|| [[Image:ThomasFowellBuxton.jpg|80px]] || [[Sir Thomas Buxton, 3rd Baronet|Sir Thomas Buxton]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR||sep=,|Bt|GCMG}} || 29 October 1895 || 29 March 1899 || {{age in years and days|1895|10|29|1899|03|29}}\n|-\n| 14|| [[Image:Ac.tennyson.jpg|80px]] || [[Hallam Tennyson, 2nd Baron Tennyson|The Rt Hon. Lord Tennyson]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR||sep=,|GCMG}} || 10 April 1899 || 17 July 1902 || {{age in years and days|1899|04|10|1902|07|17}}\n|-\n|-  bgcolor=\"#F5F5F5\"\n! colspan=\"9\" align=\"left\"|<span style=\"color:black;\">Governors appointed by [[Edward VII|King Edward VII]] (1901\u20131910):</span>\n|-\n| 15 || [[Image:GeorgeLeHunte.jpg|80px]] || [[George Le Hunte|Sir George Le Hunte]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR||sep=,|KCMG}} || 1 July 1903 || 18 February 1909 || {{age in years and days|1903|07|01|1909|02|18}}\n|-\n| 16\n| [[Image:Day Bosanquet.jpg|80px]]\n| [[Admiral (Royal Navy)|Admiral]] [[Day Bosanquet|Sir Day Bosanquet]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR||sep=,|GCVO|KCB}}\n| 18 February 1909\n| 22 March 1914\n| {{age in years and days|1909|02|18|1914|03|22}}\n|-\n|-  bgcolor=\"#F5F5F5\"\n! colspan=\"9\" align=\"left\"|<span style=\"color:black;\">Governors appointed by [[George V|King George V]] (1910\u20131936):</span>\n|-\n| 17\n| [[Image:Henry Galway.jpg|80px]]\n| [[Lieutenant colonel (United Kingdom)|Lieutenant Colonel]] [[Henry Galway|Sir Henry Galway]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR||sep=,|KCMG|DSO}}\n| 18 April 1914\n| 30 April 1920\n| {{age in years and days|1914|04|18|1920|04|30}}\n|-\n| 18\n| [[Image:William Weigall.jpg|80px]]\n| [[Lieutenant colone